description: Serving Lake Tahoe gourmet food with their big, Red Truck.After 20 years of experience in professional kitchens, chefs Larry Abney and Ramsey Etchison are loose on the streets with a big red truck serving sustainable, organic, eclectic eats.Larry Abney: Super Chef Feeding the Masses, one Hungry local at a time.Ramsey Etchison: Triple Threat Chef, Rockstar, and Social Networking Genius.Megan Lacy:Behind every great food truck, is a great woman.
name: Red Truck Tahoe
